question: Number 9 with Tony please :)
answer:
What calms them when they are upset? 

Tony calms down by letting off steam, physically. He’s a super emotional person, but doesn’t really know how to rationalise the strength of his emotions, so when he’s stressed or angry, he loves nothing more than to go down to his workshop and take it out on a spare pile of metal, or smash the glass in on his car windows, or something equally dramatic

send me a character and a number and I’ll tell you my hcs :)

summary: Remembering hurts || 2 Prolouge | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 l 5 Word count: 1216 "Heyyyy Tony" y/n slurs through the phone. She might have...
body:
Remembering hurts || 2

Prolouge | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 l 5

Word count: 1216

“Heyyyy Tony” y/n slurs through the phone. She might have had one to many drinks with Asgardian booze in it. “Andreia are you okay?” Tony asks concerned. “Yeah yeah I am fine. Just wondering. Like why am I here?” y/n’s mouth is slightly agape and a quizzical look is on her face. “What?” Tony furrows his eyebrows. “Y'know why am I your assistant and not like still on Asgard?” she wonders out loud.

“What the hell is Assgard?” Tony asks. “Nononono it’s Asgard with one s.” y/n says dragging the s. “Yes what is it?” Tony wonders. “It’s a different realm. I was born there” y/n explains. “Okay you are clearly drunk. I am coming to get you. Stay where you are” the billionaire says. “Yay my knight in shining armor!” the drunk girl beams at which Tonys heart flutter. “Just stay where you are” he orders before disconnecting the call.

Tony runs straight to one of his cars not really caring which one. The only thing he cares about now is y/n’s well being. “He jumps in a Ferrari and drives towards her destination. "Hurry up” Tony says uner his breath towards the traffic light. When the colour jumps to green he’s gone within a second. He’s soon with the drunk woman.

The billionaire sees her sitting next to some other guys, they are clearly enjoying themselves. y/n looks up to be met with the familiar geze of here boss. “Tony! What are you doing here?” she stumbles over to him. “I came to pick you up remember” he answers which gets a number of boo’s and fuck you’s from the guys. “Really? Thank you” y/n hugs him. “Let’s get you in the car.” Tony softly says.

He carefully leads y/n towards his car and places her inside. “You know you look cute” y/n blurts out suddenly. “What?” Tony tilts his head slightly. “You look cute I mean look at those eyes and your fluffy hair” y/n leans over and ruffels his hair, earning a chuckle from the bilionaire. “Why thank you. You don’t look so bad yourself either” he compliments her. “I know” The godess says confident. “Now don’t be so cocky” Tony shakes his head. “I am cocky says the man who I once herd say that his dick is too big for this world.” y/n looks at him. “You herd me that day?” Tony asks in shock. “Yup. Also nice to know that my boss thinks that I have a killer arse” y/n says proudly. “So am I ever going to know what you bought for your birthday?” the genius asks in hope to change the subject. “Oh. It’s really pretty. It’s a beautiful blue dress with a low back” the girl says not noticing how the subject suddenly changes. “really? Am I ever going to see you in it?” Tony wonders out loud. “Yeah. I want to wear it to that gala we have” Andreia beams. “The one we have in a month?” he asks. “Yes that one” y/n points at him.

“Oh my god I know this place” the girl says with admiration in her eyes. “Yes this is your apartement complex” Tony confirms. “I kew it!” she fist pumps the air. Tony chuckles at her foolish actions. “I told you you look cute” the drunk girl bops his nose. “Let’s get you inside” the billioniaire shakes his head.

Tony leads the girl to her apartement. “Y/n. can you give me your keys?” he asks her. “Yup” the girl says popping the p. Y/n hand over the keys and Tony opens the door. Together they stumble in the small apartment. It was very cozy and had a homy feeling, the exact opposite as her home in Asgard.

“You have a cute appartment” Tony coments. “Hol up, we’ve known each other for,,,,, 12 years and you’ve'n’t been here?” y/n looks bewilderd. “Has it been 17 years already?” the billionaire asks. “Yup. You were 21 when I started.” y/n thinks back of the time she first came to earth or Midgard as she called it then.

“Misses y/n. How are you today?” Fury ask. “Wonderfull. I have a job interview planned for the aft'rnoon” she says happily. “What company?” Fury questions. “Stark industries, the new ceo needs an assistant” y/n walks towards the counter. “Would you fancy some tea?” she asks. “Yes, please”.

Y/n pours in the two cups of tea. “You know you could always work for SHIELD? You are the ultimate spy” he says. The two cups slip out of her hand. The word ultimate is one of the many things she can’t stand to hear. It reminds her of the masacre and how her suster she’d grown to live killed her family. How she almost killed y/n.

“Oh my. I am terribly sorry” the godess apologizes. “It doesn’t matter. I am going anyway.” Fury says before walking out if the door.

Y/n lets out a grunt of frustation. She puts on a suit and walks to the car she got from SHIELD. She drives to SI and takes a deep breath before entering the building. Her nerves were spiking especially when she sat down next to all these beautiful women.

Y/n had her own brown hair and because growing up she couldn’t show it she has grown to be insecure about her true sight. Tony Stark walks out if the door, wearing an ACDC shirt something y/n did not expect from a billionaire. “You you and you go away” he pointed at the three girls in skimpy dresses next to the godess. “You come on in” he orderd.

“Yes sir” y/n scarmbled all her stuff together before following the man in his office. “So you’re hired” he started “I want you to start monday and be availablenat all times” he shoves a file to y/n. “Wait that’s it you don’t have to ask me anything?” She asks dumbfounded. “Oh yes yes you’re right. Uhm Miss y/n. Are you easily annoyed?” he asks her. “No bit I don’t seem why that’s important” y/n furrows her eyebrows. “You’re working with me of course it’s important. I will see you Monday. You can go now” he says.

“Remember when we met” The girl giggles “you you were so weird.” “Yes well that’s because I just met a beautiful woman” he strokes a strand if hair behind her ear. “Nah I am not. You know whe when I was young my father told me to to have blue hair with blue eyes. I had that until I moved.” Y/n slurs. “Really that’s awful” Tonys eyes widen. “That’s not even close to the worst he’s done” she waves her arms around almost falling because of the motion.

“Let’s get you to bed” Tony leads the stumbling girl to her room. y/n lifts the dress over her head and stuggles to get in the shirt Tony gives to her.

“Thank you” y/n smiles at her boss. “No problem. Bye” Tony leaves a soft kiss on her forehead before flicking the lights off. “Tony?” a soft whisper comes from the room. “Yes” he turns his head around. “Ca van you stay?” y/n asks. “Sure” he slides next to the girl. She immidately curls into his side. Tony plays with her hair before they both doze off.

“Heyyyy Tony” y/n slurs through the phone. She might have had one to many drinks with Asgardian booze in it. “Andreia are you okay?” Tony asks concerned. “Yeah yeah I am fine. Just wondering. Like why am I here?” y/n’s mouth is slightly agape and a quizzical look is on her face. “What?” Tony furrows his eyebrows. “Y'know why am I your assistant and not like still on Asgard?” she wonders out loud.

“What the hell is Assgard?” Tony asks. “Nononono it’s Asgard with one s.” y/n says dragging the s. “Yes what is it?” Tony wonders. “It’s a different realm. I was born there” y/n explains. “Okay you are clearly drunk. I am coming to get you. Stay where you are” the billionaire says. “Yay my knight in shining armor!” the drunk girl beams at which Tonys heart flutter. “Just stay where you are” he orders before disconnecting the call.

Tony runs straight to one of his cars not really caring which one. The only thing he cares about now is y/n’s well being. “He jumps in a Ferrari and drives towards her destination. "Hurry up” Tony says uner his breath towards the traffic light. When the colour jumps to green he’s gone within a second. He’s soon with the drunk woman.

The billionaire sees her sitting next to some other guys, they are clearly enjoying themselves. y/n looks up to be met with the familiar geze of here boss. “Tony! What are you doing here?” she stumbles over to him. “I came to pick you up remember” he answers which gets a number of boo’s and fuck you’s from the guys. “Really? Thank you” y/n hugs him. “Let’s get you in the car.” Tony softly says.

He carefully leads y/n towards his car and places her inside. “You know you look cute” y/n blurts out suddenly. “What?” Tony tilts his head slightly. “You look cute I mean look at those eyes and your fluffy hair” y/n leans over and ruffels his hair, earning a chuckle from the bilionaire. “Why thank you. You don’t look so bad yourself either” he compliments her. “I know” The godess says confident. “Now don’t be so cocky” Tony shakes his head. “I am cocky says the man who I once herd say that his dick is too big for this world.” y/n looks at him. “You herd me that day?” Tony asks in shock. “Yup. Also nice to know that my boss thinks that I have a killer arse” y/n says proudly. “So am I ever going to know what you bought for your birthday?” the genius asks in hope to change the subject. “Oh. It’s really pretty. It’s a beautiful blue dress with a low back” the girl says not noticing how the subject suddenly changes. “really? Am I ever going to see you in it?” Tony wonders out loud. “Yeah. I want to wear it to that gala we have” Andreia beams. “The one we have in a month?” he asks. “Yes that one” y/n points at him.

“Oh my god I know this place” the girl says with admiration in her eyes. “Yes this is your apartement complex” Tony confirms. “I kew it!” she fist pumps the air. Tony chuckles at her foolish actions. “I told you you look cute” the drunk girl bops his nose. “Let’s get you inside” the billioniaire shakes his head.

Tony leads the girl to her apartement. “Y/n. can you give me your keys?” he asks her. “Yup” the girl says popping the p. Y/n hand over the keys and Tony opens the door. Together they stumble in the small apartment. It was very cozy and had a homy feeling, the exact opposite as her home in Asgard.

“You have a cute appartment” Tony coments. “Hol up, we’ve known each other for,,,,, 12 years and you’ve'n’t been here?” y/n looks bewilderd. “Has it been 17 years already?” the billionaire asks. “Yup. You were 21 when I started.” y/n thinks back of the time she first came to earth or Midgard as she called it then.

“Misses y/n. How are you today?” Fury ask. “Wonderfull. I have a job interview planned for the aft'rnoon” she says happily. “What company?” Fury questions. “Stark industries, the new ceo needs an assistant” y/n walks towards the counter. “Would you fancy some tea?” she asks. “Yes, please”.

Y/n pours in the two cups of tea. “You know you could always work for SHIELD? You are the ultimate spy” he says. The two cups slip out of her hand. The word ultimate is one of the many things she can’t stand to hear. It reminds her of the masacre and how her suster she’d grown to live killed her family. How she almost killed y/n.

“Oh my. I am terribly sorry” the godess apologizes. “It doesn’t matter. I am going anyway.” Fury says before walking out if the door.

Y/n lets out a grunt of frustation. She puts on a suit and walks to the car she got from SHIELD. She drives to SI and takes a deep breath before entering the building. Her nerves were spiking especially when she sat down next to all these beautiful women.

Y/n had her own brown hair and because growing up she couldn’t show it she has grown to be insecure about her true sight. Tony Stark walks out if the door, wearing an ACDC shirt something y/n did not expect from a billionaire. “You you and you go away” he pointed at the three girls in skimpy dresses next to the godess. “You come on in” he orderd.

“Yes sir” y/n scarmbled all her stuff together before following the man in his office. “So you’re hired” he started “I want you to start monday and be availablenat all times” he shoves a file to y/n. “Wait that’s it you don’t have to ask me anything?” She asks dumbfounded. “Oh yes yes you’re right. Uhm Miss y/n. Are you easily annoyed?” he asks her. “No bit I don’t seem why that’s important” y/n furrows her eyebrows. “You’re working with me of course it’s important. I will see you Monday. You can go now” he says.

“Remember when we met” The girl giggles “you you were so weird.” “Yes well that’s because I just met a beautiful woman” he strokes a strand if hair behind her ear. “Nah I am not. You know whe when I was young my father told me to to have blue hair with blue eyes. I had that until I moved.” Y/n slurs. “Really that’s awful” Tonys eyes widen. “That’s not even close to the worst he’s done” she waves her arms around almost falling because of the motion.

“Let’s get you to bed” Tony leads the stumbling girl to her room. y/n lifts the dress over her head and stuggles to get in the shirt Tony gives to her.

“A broad, soft hand cupped his face, keeping him from continuing his barrage of praise, of thanks. Eyes wide, concerned, expression fading away to…to adoration, before pulling him up for a bruising kiss.

‘Let me take care of you.’ Whispered in his ear, God, so gentle. Tony felt tears in his eyes.”

It’s Tony’s turn to be reassured that he’s safe and loved.
